		<h4>Benefits of my Health Records</h4>
Coming from different backgrounds people are unaware of the benefits provided by MY HEALTH RECORDS.
<ol>
 	<li>Over the web, through a desktop, tablet or mobile phone web browser</li>
 	<li>Through hospital and practice-based clinical information systems that are My Health Record-ready.</li>
</ol><h4>Guide to setup My Health Record account</h4>
